Package: CeDExplorer
Title: Celiac Disease Gene Expression and GWAS Analysis Toolkit
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Yuxi", "Zhang", email = "your.email@utoronto.ca", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: An R package for integrated analysis of celiac disease genetic and expression data. 
    Provides tools for GWAS visualization, gene expression analysis, inflammation signature 
    scoring, and HLA association studies to support celiac disease research.
